Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:51.20,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Every trial we overcome brings a chance for thrills. (I can't stay)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:56.05,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow and each day after will be heated, intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:59.92,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,A chain of excitements!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:02.49,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,That's right! Shining! Running! Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:05.23,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Trust your curiosity, follow your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:10.70,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,and head for your goal, that's what adventure is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.40,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Let's go shining! Running! Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:16.12,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Spread open the chart of your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:19.17,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,There's power hidden in the bond between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:22.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,it'll help us grasp the end of our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.96,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Never! Never! Never! Never stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:30.16,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We are the one! Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:39.91,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Kyros is fighting the mysterious gladiator, Ricky, who appeared out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.68,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Kyros wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:47.52,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,After nine years, he has finally won three thousand consecutive fights! He is undefeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:53.39,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Kyros, the living legend, is the very definition of the word "invincible"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:56.50,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Why did you fight without telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.63,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,King Riku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:04.17,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I wanted to teach you a lesson. I was quite strong, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:09.68,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,That said, you held back knowing it was me.\NYou're a failure as a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.68,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Isn't this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:19.85,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,You've kept your own life locked away in this cage for nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:21.69,Title,,0,0,430,,{\fad(1500,0)}Dressrosa in Turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.66,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Come out. There's a job I want to entrust to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:31.93,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Kyros, rather than regretting your past, you can move on and protect lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.03,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Isn't that a better way of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:38.60,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.52,Main,Crowd,0,0,2,,Kyros, we're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:50.82,Captions,Caption,0,0,175,,{\fad(467,233)}One year later
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.42,Main,Crowd,0,0,2,,Kyros, thank you for all you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.59,Captions,Caption,0,0,240,,{\fad(1001,0)}Dressrosa's Riku Royal Army Captain\NKyros (25 years old)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:58.92,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kyros-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.70,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,You're quite popular, huh, Kyros-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.37,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,But you're still a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:12.47,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,I can't fathom why my father would let you into the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.92,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,{\i1}P-Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.88,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Sister, don't bring up his old scars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.62,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,And then he makes you the captain of the army, with the job of upholding the law...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.11,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,He must be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.51,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:26.82,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,{\an8}You may have the rest of the country fooled, but not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:34.43,Captions,Caption,0,0,240,,{\fad(2002,0)}Crown Princess of Dressrosa\NScarlett (Fifteen years old)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.95,Main,Scarlett,0,0,2,,Someday, I'll expose you for what you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:34.43,Main,Scarlett,0,0,2,,Stay away from us! Do you understand?{ So much text over text. Changed "me and my sister" to just "us" so it would be one line. -Btwb }
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.60,Main,Violet,0,0,2,,But Sister, he's actually really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:39.30,Captions,Caption,0,0,240,,{\fad(500,0)}Second in line (Younger sister)\NViola (Ten years old)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.67,Main,Scarlett,0,0,2,,Hey, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.77,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,His mind is obviously filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:45.77,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,But... I'm supposed to protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.51,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.36,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Scarlett-sama has been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.44,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,It's pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.78,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,What happened to her escorts?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.08,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,They've all been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:57.08,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.45,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.23,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I-I'm so, so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.93,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to touch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:18.47,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,Kyros! I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.51,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.68,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,She's cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.78,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,What brought this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.12,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Oh, I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:48.07,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,What?! You resign as my daughters' bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:51.10,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,You couldn't be in love with Scarlett, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.94,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.57,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,N-No, of course not. Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:05:04.06,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Some of the citizens might give you their blessings, but this goes against the country's ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.69,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,That's just what the general masses are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:11.39,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,Father! If I can't marry him, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.46,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,I will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.32,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,Scarlett-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:29.01,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,She died of a sudden illness. I'm sure she would have made a wonderful queen someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.41,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:37.68,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Starting today, you are no longer a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:40.92,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Society believes you are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.22,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:47.33,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm disrespecting all you've done for me, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.83,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Indeed, this is unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.27,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Or it would be, for anyone but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.74,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Kyros, this is completely unheard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.35,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,Her name will be Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.78,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,Kyros, hold her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.38,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,She's your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.45,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I can't touch something so pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:19.36,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,My hands are filthy! I don't want to corrupt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.70,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,What a funny father you have, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.17,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Rebecca, you're like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.71,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I'll be with you. I'll always watch over you! {I actually flipped the order of sentences around here, but seeing how he uses the phrasing "itsudemo kimi no soba ni iru" here, which (despite actually meaning "I will always be beside you") has been previously translated as "...will always watch over you", I wanted to maintain consistency and such. So note Xemnas, this is entirely intentional. Do not change. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.98,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I'm your grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.52,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.56,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Rebecca, how you've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.25,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,Father, will you take that mask off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.55,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Kyros.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.35,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Gloves! I need my gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.36,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,You're such a cutie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.66,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,You're crying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.81,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,The royal palace... it's burning. {Copy-paste from 651}{ I know this has been seen before, but it seems weird to have two Flashback styled lines while the rest of the line in the same scene are Main. -Btwb }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:14.08,Main,Scarlett,0,0,0,,What's happening to this country? {End copy-paste from 651}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.88,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I'll go to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:18.18,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett, Rebecca, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.45,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:23.92,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,If the danger reaches here,\Nthen wait for me at the red flower field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.12,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I swear I'll come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.67,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.67,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,What have you done to \Nthis country and the king, pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:45.28,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,The king burned the city. Didn't you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.95,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,His Majesty would never do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.95,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:57.59,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Take this Sea Stone chain off me! I'm not a Devil Fruit user. {I wanna know who in that room could have fastened the chains -Kae}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:08:01.56,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Kyros, your reputation precedes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.86,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:09.37,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,The king will be replaced, and the old royal family will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:16.34,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,My men should already be going after your wife and daughter, who carry the blood of the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.20,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:24.92,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Dressrosa's time under the Riku family is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.09,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,He cut off his own leg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.03,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.61,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,A toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.12,Main,Buffalo,0,0,0,,That toy just ran off with the king -{\i1}dasuyan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.59,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,I've been turned into a toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.72,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,What's going on? Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.93,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,King Riku! It's me, Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:14.60,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I've never heard that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:21.11,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,I'll forever be in your debt, strange, little toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:25.68,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Run, Scarlett, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:28.55,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Wait for me at the promised place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:36.22,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,Nobody knows my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.70,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,I must get to the red flower field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.95,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett and Rebecca are waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.58,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett? {Yeah seriously, what are the odds that she would just happen to get shot RIGHT IN FRONT OF HIM? -Starfish} {stfu already - Sewil}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.22,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.69,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:22.70,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Somebody's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.57,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The Riku Royal Army again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:30.44,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,Why? Why didn't you wait for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.28,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:42.92,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,I must have disappeared from your mind too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.39,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,Both our promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.26,Thoughts,Kyros,0,0,0,,and our time together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:57.54,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:02.77,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.21,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Scarlett! Scarlett!
