Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:56.88,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh? But that's a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:24:03.02,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,All the toys used to be human. They'd been erased from our memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:08.89,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Now that Sugar has been defeated, our memories have returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.23,0:24:16.27,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,He is the former captain of the Riku Royal Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:17.34,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.57,0:24:24.14,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,The mightiest warrior in the history of the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.54,0:24:26.86,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Isn't he the guy on that statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:30.41,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Yes, that's him. And he's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:33.52,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,Rebecca's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:36.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Huh? But she said she'd never met him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.15,0:24:38.14,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,All these years while he'd been forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:41.96,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,he had no way of telling her who he really was!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.96,0:24:47.06,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,He's been watching over his beloved daughter for a decade!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.34,0:25:02.98,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,He's stayed by her side every single day as a toy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.99,0:25:13.42,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.54,0:25:19.93,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:21.33,Main,Riku,0,0,0,,Kyros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:22.53,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.44,0:25:28.74,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have kept you waiting for ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.31,0:25:32.91,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I'm here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.80,0:25:56.33,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,I've come to restore the true Dressrosa!{did he really just die as cleanly and unceremoniously as that? if so, I'm just so incredibly pleased. that's awesome. -Kae}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.11,0:26:08.21,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,Ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.98,0:26:13.28,Main,Kyros,0,0,0,,We've had to endure your rule for ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.55,0:26:17.96,Main,Grunts,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doflamingo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.96,0:26:20.09,Main,Buffalo,0,0,0,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.09,0:26:21.16,Main,Buffalo,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.40,0:26:27.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Mingo died!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.16,0:26:29.40,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But I wanted to send him flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.40,0:26:30.33,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,I see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.33,0:26:31.54,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Over there! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.54,0:26:32.32,Main,Violet,0,0,0,,We've been spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.32,0:26:33.50,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.71,0:26:36.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's save Traf!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.08,0:26:41.61,Captions,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(302,0)\pos(1035.691,90.5)}Corrida Colosseum
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.12,0:26:48.45,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,What's a gorilla doing in the spectators' seats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.45,0:26:50.09,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.59,0:26:52.49,Main,Diamante,0,0,0,,This is a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.06,0:26:57.16,Main,Diamante,0,0,0,,Trebol, you were supposed to keep an eye on Sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.16,0:26:58.33,Main,Diamante,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.33,0:27:00.66,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Hey, you done crying yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.66,0:27:02.37,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I ain't your babysitter. {Cecil: Barto is so cool!}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.37,0:27:03.90,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,You don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.17,0:27:06.60,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.14,0:27:10.31,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I have a father!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.31,0:27:15.78,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,That seems to have been this country's secret, Rebecca.{"That" presumably being the whole collective amnesia-deal. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.92,0:27:22.29,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,Everything has a core. {Cecil: He means heart/centre/secret/weak spot I assume?}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.09,0:27:24.52,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,As long as you dig enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.52,0:27:29.79,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Now you're spouting confusing nonsense too, grand senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.90,0:27:32.76,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,The same goes for this arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.70,0:27:35.37,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,It has a core.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.20,0:27:40.77,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,How about we put an end to this match?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.98,0:27:51.65,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Dragon Claw Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.65,0:27:58.86,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Dragon's Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.96,0:28:11.44,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Amazing! Lucy's attack is unbelievably powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.44,0:28:13.24,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The arena is sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.31,0:28:16.44,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The arena exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.74,0:28:22.15,Main,Burgess,0,0,0,,I'm losing my footing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.28,0:28:25.62,Main,Diamante,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.62,0:28:28.19,Main,Sabo,0,0,0,,Something came up. I'm going to win now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.62,0:28:31.56,Main,Koala,0,0,0,,Oh.{Is it just me or is there something... off... about her face in this scene? -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:34.76,Main,Hack,0,0,0,,I heard a really loud noise from up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.76,0:28:35.79,Main,Koala,0,0,0,,Hack?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.79,0:28:37.70,Main,Hack,0,0,0,,Did he do something crazy again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.96,0:28:41.43,Main,Koala,0,0,0,,He's on his way to the underground now.
